madeShotThreshold.description: defaults to five which means, at 95% and above, a shot is made

sliderTimeInput.description: amount of time slider takes going one way. will change based on position on the court

streakThreshold.description: how many shots need to be made in a row to get a streak

positionOne.description: position of camera on first shot

rotationOne.description: rotation of camera on first shot

positionTwo.description: rotation of camera on second shot

rotationTwo.description: rotation of camera on second shot

positionThree.description: rotation of camera on third shot

rotationThree.description: rotation of camera on third shot

positionFour.description: rotation of camera on fourth shot

rotationFour.description: rotation of camera on fourth shot

positionFive.description: rotation of camera on fifth shot

rotationFive.description: rotation of camera on fifth shot

initialTime.description: needs an integer. shot clock time for a game.

cageOffDiffuse.description: diffuse color of cage when nothing is happening. normalized rgb

cageOnDiffuse.description: diffuse color of cage when shot clock goes off. normalized rgb
